Yeah that&#39;s true.  But it&#39;s sooo cool to go to a place out in the middle 
of nowhere, miles from even simple things like electric lines and radio 
towers, and get EVP responses which actually give logical answers to your 
questions. It &quot;could&quot; be anything but the probability is that it is only 
certain things. It is most likely NOT someone with a radio or other 
electronic device fooling with you.

Zack

